node.text:
To be frank—the last 6 months or so have been super tough. Not stoked on it. That said, life will always have its challenges and I feel my job is to attack those challenges with the best attitude possible. Excited to get back out there soon!

Shot on my @gopro.

node.text: Having a blast at the track last week! Thanks @dirtshark for coming out and shooting this one. Not too long until MEC. @monsterenergy
Won a moto pushing the ole girl up the finish today. 🤣 Tried my ass off but came up a little short on the overall. Fans were unreal. I missed you guys!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Adam Cianciarulo on April 16, 2021 tagging @stjude, and @supercrosslive. May be an image of 1 person, standing and text that says 'm Kawasaki Kawasaki WE> WON'T STOP'.

node.text: It’s an honor to use our platform as racers to bring attention to a great cause. I have all the respect in the world for the kids, their families and the people @stjude fighting this good fight! #StJudeWontStop until no child dies from cancer. I’m proud to support the @stjude mission with @SupercrossLIVE. Join me and get your shirt! Visit www.stjude.org/supercross or text “SUPER” to 785-833.
